JAVASCRIPT
(Please tells us what the JavaScript does e.g. "click on the green button and it does the following...")
----------
1. Form validation: When submitting the contact form, it validates the required fields and displays alerts if they're empty or invalid.
2. Interactive grid items: Clicking on stat grid items toggles their background color to the accent color.
3. Dark/Light mode toggle: A button in the bottom right corner toggles between dark and light mode.
4. BMI Calculator: Entering height and weight and clicking "Calculate" computes and displays BMI with category.
5. Body Fat Calculator: Entering measurements and clicking "Calculate" computes body fat percentage using the U.S. Navy method.
6. Gender selection in Body Fat Calculator shows/hides the hip measurement field when switching between male and female.

NOTES TO STAFF
(If there is anything you need to tell us, please use the section below)
---------------
The body fat calculator uses the simplified U.S. Navy formula with conversion from cm to inches.


